<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="everyone-pron">everyone <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'evriwʌn/    美 /'evriwʌn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>每个人；人人：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In a small village everyone knows everyone else. 
在小村子里，人人都相识。</p></div>

<p>注: 句中常用they或he指代everybody / everyone。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Everyone has their / his duty. 
人人都有自己的职责。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>You can ask anyone for help. <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ here is willing to lend you a hand.   （2014 安徽）<br />
A.One <br />
B.No one<br />
C.Everyone<br />
D.Someone  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. C  </p></div>